&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Work closely with a named list of enterprise prospect accounts, using a consultative approach to identify pain points that Forter&#39;s Identity Intelligence platform can solve&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Actively understand each customer&#39;s technology footprint, strategic growth plans, business drivers, technology strategy, and competitive landscape&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Drive business development, forecast accurately, and achieve strategic goals by leading customers through the full sales cycle — from prospecting through close&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Collaborate with internal teams and Pre-sales Solutions Consultants to create customized presentations and tailored ROI models&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
