&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;6-12 months of previous business experience highly preferred&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Excellent written and verbal communication skills to be effective in positioning a clear, concise and well-understood message&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
