&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Ability to navigate systems and tools and follow process&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Highly-motivated and driven individual who thrives working toward monthly and quarterly quotas&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
