&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;This is a unique opportunity to own the end-to-end AI transformation of entire functions, with executive sponsorship and real mandate. You’ll be working as part of an incredibly strong team of senior engineers at the forefront of AI. The work revolves around learning the latest tech in AI, and leveraging it to change how hundreds of people across the organization work every day.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;You&#39;ll operate with unusual autonomy: scoping problems directly with function leaders, deciding what to build, shipping it, measuring impact, and iterating. You&#39;ll work closely with senior leadership to ensure your work aligns with company strategy, giving you company-wide business impact and visibility.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
