&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Develop and maintain our internal MCP server that easily and securely exposes Forter’s vast data stores to AI agents.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Create and implement robust evaluation frameworks and AI guardrails to safeguard Forter’s value and ensure model reliability.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Establish deep expertise and sustainable AI engineering practices.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 12pt;&quot;&gt;Promote AI readiness and track adoption across the company to build lasting impact.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
